name: The Un̴k̸n̶o̷w̵n D̵o̸m̴i̸n̷ 3
description: The Unknown Domain is an ongoing collection of ǝʌıʇɐɹnɓıɟ-ıɯǝs and abstract surreal illustrations created using fre domain original scanned artworks (CC0 licence) from French artists that range from the 15th to the 19th century, following the principle of compositing cells and layers as textures for each piece creating a final composition made from the multiplied overlayed iterated textures of each artist original work.
